{
  "stem": "11167.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she used you say, if so and so will come, let me know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- but it was-- I-- I didn't let her know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Friday I decided I'm going to my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had $10 with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I find it-- I find it-- where this-- where the buses stays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went, and I ask-- I ask him in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say to him, would you like to take me to this and this place?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have only $10.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He laughed at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, you don't need it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he took me to Rishon LeZion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] is a street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is the [INAUDIBLE] from our man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he did give the name of it, he said, here is [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dror, ?] where you must go down, and that is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you will find your sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She collapsed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She really couldn't-- she couldn't-- she didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was looking good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a rest on the-- on the ship, already-- in the boat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was prepared myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had a pair of flannel trousers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had a little jersey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was looking good, because I-- I had already what to eat, and picked up weight-- from 42 kilos, I weighed already 50.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was different.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I spent with her, the-- the Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was still the blackout-- we couldn't have the-- the lights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Still in Israel, was still the fighting, when I came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was still with no lights, and you had to-- the bombs still did go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Arabs they didn't let us live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was staying only Friday, Friday night, Saturday and Sunday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there, I met my cousin.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
